\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b \cf0 NNM.LeapMotion.device.amxd
\f2\b0  (Max Audio Effect)\
Connect to a Leap Motion controller, and sends tracking data to other devices.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
